Description
This is a metabolism model of Staphylococcus aureus subsp. aureus N315 in SBML format.
iSB619
The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort. This file has been exported from the software COBRApy and further processed with a JSBML-based application.
This file has been produced by the Systems Biology Research Group and is currently hosted on BiGG knowledgebase and identified by: iSB619.
